                Yeastar Click to Call works?</title>
            <p>Yeastar Click to Call strictly follows the steps below to work.</p>
            <p>
                <ol id="ol_s44_5ys_xjb">
                    <li>Detect phone number. Yeastar Click to Call detects phone numbers in web
                        pages or CRMs and turns detected phone numbers into clickable links with
                        underlines highlighted.<p>Hover your mouse over the detected phone number,
                            and a floating window will display, prompting you to call the phone
                            number with Linkus.</p><p><image id="image_slx_f1t_xjb"
                                href="../Images/admin/highlight-phone-number.png"/></p></li>
                    <li>Click the phone number that you want to dial. A window pops up as
                                below:<p><image id="image_wl5_p1t_xjb"
                                href="../Images/admin/click-to-call-select-linkus.png"/></p></li>
                    <li>Click <uicontrol>Linkus</uicontrol>. Linkus will place the call
                                immediately.<p><image id="image_o1v_ry1_yjb"
                                href="../Images/admin/linkus-call.png"/></p></li>
                </ol>
            </p>
